## Implementation Order

Requirements are implemented in dependency order. Each phase assumes the previous phase is complete.

### Phase 1: Fix the foundation

*Goal: Every number on screen is correct.*

|Step|Implements|What to do                                                                           |
|----|----------|-------------------------------------------------------------------------------------|
|1   |R1.1      |Remove `Budget.spent` field. Compute from transactions on read.                      |
|2   |R1.2, R6.1|Fix fixed expense matching. Match by categoryId within current month, not exact date.|
|3   |R1.3      |Verify amount signs enforced at API level for all mutation endpoints.                |
|4   |R7.3      |Re-test AI insights with corrected budget data.                                      |

