|10  |R3.3, R4.3–R4.5       |Add “By Person” and “By Property” views to Spending page. Add property filter to Transactions.|
|11  |R7.1, R7.6, R7.7      |Add MonthlySnapshot model + cron. Generate baseline on first import.                          |
